  "payload": {
    "body_html": "<div data-oe-version=\"2.0\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border-style:none;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;caption-side:bottom;border-radius: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n  <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n    <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n      <td align=\"center\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#111827;border-bottom-color:#111827;border-right-color:#111827;border-top-color:#111827;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;padding: 20px 0px; background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;caption-side:bottom;border-collapse: collapse; max-width: 600px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n          <tbody style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n            <tr style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;\">\n              <td style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#808080;border-bottom-color:#808080;border-right-color:#808080;border-top-color:#808080;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;padding: 20px; background-color: #f2f2f2; color: #101820;\">\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Dear\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">\n                    <t t-esc=\"object.partner_name or 'Applicant'\"/>\n                  </b>,\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  We encountered a technical issue that may have prevented your application information form from being submitted successfully.\n                  <br/><br/>\n                  To proceed with your application for the\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-esc=\"object.job_id.name or 'Position'\"/></b>\n                  position at\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\"><t t-esc=\"object.job_id.company_id.name or 'Our Company'\"/></b>,\n                  we kindly ask you to submit the form again using the link below.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">What you need to do:</b><br/>\n                  - Please complete the short form again (about <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">5 minutes</b>).<br/>\n                  - If you already tried before, we still need a fresh submission due to the issue.<br/>\n                  - If you run into any problems, reply to this email and we\u2019ll help.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <t t-set=\"survey_link\" t-value=\"ctx.get('survey_link') or '#'\"/>\n\n                <div style=\"padding:16px 8px;\">\n                  <a t-att-href=\"survey_link\" style=\"color: #101820; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin: 0px; background-color: #ec008c; text-decoration: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;\"><font style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;color: #101820;\">&nbsp;<font style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#ffffff;border-bottom-color:#ffffff;border-right-color:#ffffff;border-top-color:#ffffff;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;color:#ffffff;\">Resubmit Your Information</font>&nbsp;</font></a></div>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Thank you for your time, and we apologize for the inconvenience.\n                </p>\n\n                <br/>\n\n                <p style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;margin:0; padding:0;\">\n                  Best regards,<br/>\n                  <b style=\"border-radius:0px;border-style:none;padding:0px;margin:0px;box-sizing:border-box;border-left-color:#101820;border-bottom-color:#101820;border-right-color:#101820;border-top-color:#101820;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;border-right-width:0px;border-top-width:0px;font-weight:bolder;\">The Recruitment Team</b>\n                </p>\n\n              </td>\n            </tr>\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n</div>",
    "email_from": "{{ object.company_id.x_studio_short_name }} <{{ object.company_id.alias_domain_id.default_from_email }}>",
